title: Spinal cord injury in Vietnamese combat.
summary: This report deals with the experience gained by observation and treatment of 114 Vietnamese combat injuries from December 1965 to April 1969. The report covers all aspects of rehabilitation, medical, physical and socio-economic....
abstract: This report deals with the experience gained by observation and treatment of 114 Vietnamese combat injuries from December 1965 to April 1969. The report covers all aspects of rehabilitation, medical, physical and socio-economic.
